<div class="grid-system">
  <div class="grid-form1 questions">
    <p>Do you want to make money from you app? Sign up on AdMob and integrate your ad codes below. We would optimzie your ads and maximize your revenue. Its pretty simple and straight forward process to signup on AdMob.
    </p>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <form class="form-horizontal" action="get_monetize" method="POST">
          <input type='hidden' name='authenticity_token' value='" + token + "'>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-sm-2 control-label hor-form">Platform</label>
            <div class="col-sm-10">
              <select class="form-control1" name="platform">
                  <option>AdMob</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="inputEmail3" class="col-sm-2 control-label hor-form">Phone Ad Unit</label>
            <div class="col-sm-10">
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="phone_ad_unit" id="inputEmail3" placeholder="Enter Phone Ad Unit">
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-sm-2 control-label hor-form">App Name</label>
            <div class="col-sm-10">
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="phone_ad_unit" id="inputEmail3" value="<%=@apps.app_name%>" readonly >
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="inputEmail3" class="col-sm-2 control-label hor-form">Interstitial Ad Unit ID</label>
            <div class="col-sm-10">
              <input type="text" class="form-control" name="add_unit_id" id="inputEmail3" placeholder="Enter Interstitial Ad Unit ID">
            </div>
          </div>          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-sm-2 control-label hor-form">Interval</label>
            <div class="col-sm-10">
              <select class="form-control1" name="interval">
                  <option>2</option>
                  <option>3</option>
                  <option>4</option>
                  <option>5</option>
                  <option>6</option>
                  <option>7</option>
                  <option>8</option>
                  <option>9</option>
                  <option>10</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div> 
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Save Changes</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
